	"Sets a flat bias against tokens that have appeared at least once. A higher value (e.g., 1.5) will penalize repetitions more strongly, while a lower value (e.g., 0.9) will be more lenient. At 0, it is disabled.": "Iestata fiksГ„вЂњtu novirzi pret tokeniem, kas ir parГ„ВЃdГ„В«juГ…ВЎies vismaz vienu reizi. AugstГ„ВЃka vГ„вЂњrtГ„В«ba (piem., 1.5) stingrГ„ВЃk sodГ„В«s atkГ„ВЃrtojumus, bet zemГ„ВЃka vГ„вЂњrtГ„В«ba (piem., 0.9) bГ…В«s iecietГ„В«gГ„ВЃka. Pie 0 tas ir atspГ„вЂњjots.",
	"Sets a scaling bias against tokens to penalize repetitions, based on how many times they have appeared. A higher value (e.g., 1.5) will penalize repetitions more strongly, while a lower value (e.g., 0.9) will be more lenient. At 0, it is disabled.": "Iestata mГ„вЂњrogojamu novirzi pret tokeniem, lai sodГ„В«tu atkГ„ВЃrtojumus, pamatojoties uz to, cik reizes tie ir parГ„ВЃdГ„В«juГ…ВЎies. AugstГ„ВЃka vГ„вЂњrtГ„В«ba (piem., 1.5) stingrГ„ВЃk sodГ„В«s atkГ„ВЃrtojumus, bet zemГ„ВЃka vГ„вЂњrtГ„В«ba (piem., 0.9) bГ…В«s iecietГ„В«gГ„ВЃka. Pie 0 tas ir atspГ„вЂњjots.",
	"Sets how far back for the model to look back to prevent repetition.": "Iestata, cik tГ„ВЃlu atpakaГ„Вј modelim skatГ„В«ties, lai novГ„вЂњrstu atkГ„ВЃrtoГ…ВЎanos.",
	"Sets the random number seed to use for generation. Setting this to a specific number will make the model generate the same text for the same prompt.": "Iestata nejauГ…ВЎo skaitГ„Вјu sГ„вЂњklu, ko izmantot Г„ВЈenerГ„вЂњГ…ВЎanai. Iestatot to uz konkrГ„вЂњtu skaitli, modelis Г„ВЈenerГ„вЂњs tГ„ВЃdu paГ…ВЎu tekstu tai paГ…ВЎai uzvednei.",
	"Sets the size of the context window used to generate the next token.": "Iestata konteksta loga izmГ„вЂњru, kas tiek izmantots nГ„ВЃkamГ„ВЃ tokena Г„ВЈenerГ„вЂњГ…ВЎanai.",
	"Sets the stop sequences to use. When this pattern is encountered, the LLM will stop generating text and return. Multiple stop patterns may be set by specifying multiple separate stop parameters in a modelfile.": "Iestata izmantojamГ„ВЃs apstГ„ВЃГ…ВЎanГ„ВЃs secГ„В«bas. Kad Г…ВЎis patterns tiek sastapts, LLM pГ„ВЃrtrauks teksta Г„ВЈenerГ„вЂњГ…ВЎanu un atgriezГ„В«s rezultГ„ВЃtu. VairГ„ВЃkus apstГ„ВЃГ…ВЎanГ„ВЃs paternus var iestatГ„В«t, norГ„ВЃdot vairГ„ВЃkus atseviГ…ВЎГ„В·us apstГ„ВЃГ…ВЎanГ„ВЃs parametrus modeГ„ВјfailГ„ВЃ.",
